snippet.title: Oddworld: Soulstorm first Teaser Trailer featuring Gameplay
snippet.description:
Sign up to the Oddworld Mailing list to get the latest news on Soulstorm: http://www.oddworld.com/signup

In this first Teaser Trailer, we show gameplay elements from Oddworld: Soulstorm for the first time.
